channel.title: Real Cleaned WinterLove Server
channel.description:
Hello all, this is a basic and clean WinterLove server, I have removed TPC and cleaned out mostly everything else.
Credits:
Me Graham Ben All the other people who have created what we have now for a WinterLove server.
There will be no pictures as it has nearly no features. It also still has some stuff left in it so don't complain about it.
Download Link: http://www.mediafire.com/?iz4vmiiemw0

item.title: Real Cleaned WinterLove Server
item.dc:creator: @doom_j doom_j
item.description:
@doom_j wrote:

[quote=“cocoa, post:12, topic:345671”][quote author=jmood128 link=topic=442057.msg3246738#msg3246738 date=1277428392]
What you mean its still messy, this is a hell of a lot cleaner. I left some stuff as references for you guys like the many int’s in the Player class. I should also add in this has saving and load through .txt files and not .dat. I know there are some things that should be taken out to make it even cleaner but I thought they would still be needed for further development.
[/quote]
Remove .txt file character file loading. It’s the worst way to do it. Every server does it and it needs to be loading through SQL of some sort. Just set up SQL tables and load them there. It’ll be more compact and load better and faster.[/quote]

Good suggestion, I only keep it text since most people use that since they have to edit all their shit.
